Udemy — Udemy Clone 🎓
A pixel-perfect, responsive clone of the Udemy e-learning platform, built from scratch using pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

Features
Responsive navbar with search bar
Hero banner with promotional card overlay
Course recommendation grid (4-column layout)
Topics recommended section
Multi-section course listings
Responsive footer with links
Tech Stack
HTML5 · CSS3 · JavaScript · VS Code · Live Server

